{"tid":1334923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試著說保皇黨，不要說建制派","createTime":"2019-07-20T09:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T02:55:22.000Z","uid":93958,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4ecda76dddc21be41cec6245e6916f0b6d5bb1f0","tid":1334923,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"建制建制，講乜撚建制派<br />\n講到好似好撚有建設性咁<br />\n保皇黨都識叫所有非我族類做反對派啦<br />\n<br />\n日講夜講反對派，d人真係以為所有非建制只識反對，冇建設<br />\n<br />\n建議所有偏黃媒體/議員，全部改口叫佢地賣港賊/保皇黨/西環傀儡<br />\n<br />\n泛民咁多年黎就係太乾手淨腳，只識講道理，唔識用文宣去增加支持，仲用自己把口叫人地建制咁多年<br />\n<br />\n好心啦，全部同我改口！<br />\n<br />\n文宣之戰，由正名開始！"},{"pid":"81498031a335ee06221c478da8b3e5c13f51b587","tid":1334923,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd7dad02e48cd96fe8e83b9c66b544066f5cb43","tid":1334923,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698f862617d7fdf15b703b153e943d1fc5802ee6","tid":1334923,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30be7e4e160c9d5cc30c5b9651dd0fcc20b6137d","tid":1334923,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgPeSgA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgPeSgA.jpg&h=0b548ae2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cbb44e560be9c1a0c88424f8d5e8eb5fcbb2de9","tid":1334923,"uid":84751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"保皇黨"},{"pid":"0929440b7777ec77b89353480991bef337a28c44","tid":1334923,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"保皇黨/親中派"},{"pid":"4e1c3ffe8a75e68987c9ecf405888d118828afdd","tid":1334923,"uid":2